E'Who%20dares%20disturb%20my%20slumber%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20animated%20character%20Vincent%20Valentine.%20Voice%20actor%20Matthew%20Mercer%20(right)%20voices%20the%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%3A%20Rebirth.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618a26616bde8d4ead82ef4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Mercer%2C%20of%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Legend%20of%20Zelda%3A%20Tears%20of%20the%20Kingdom%26quot%3B%20fame%2C%20voices%20Vincent%20Valentine.%3Cp%3ESquare%20Enix%3B%20Gregg%20DeGuire%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMercer's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC1h3ufMcS2Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopening%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%3A%20Rebirth%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20a%20fandom%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20deep%20growl%20of%20%26quot%3BWho%20dares%20disturb%20my%20slumber%3F%26quot%3B%20from%20within%20the%20depths%20of%20his%20velvet-lined%20coffin%2C%20longtime%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%26quot%3B%20fans%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20super-cool%2C%20uber-goth%20gunslinger.%20(Spoiler%20alert%3A%20Valentine%20looks%20like%20a%20vampire.%20But%20he's%20not%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20in%20the%20strictest%20definition%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%94%20he%20just%20has%20multiple%20monstrous%20forms%2C%20and%20takes%20long%20rests%20in%20a%20casket.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20is%20like%20the%20dark%20edge%20lord%20of%20emo%20sadness%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20and%20then%20has%20this%20kind%20of%20burning%20fire%20of%20passion%20on%20the%20inside%20that%20begins%20to%20kindle%20as%20his%20story%20revs%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20a%20thought%20in%20my%20head%20of%20how%20he%2