%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20stock%20plummeted%20by%20more%20than%2050%25%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGlobal%20Life%20and%20a%20subsidiary%20now%20face%20DOJ%20subpoenas%20over%20potential%20wrongdoing%20at%20a%20leading%20agency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20insurance%20giant%20is%20floundering%20after%20Business%20Insider%20reported%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20potential%20wrongdoing%20at%20a%20leading%20sales%20agency%20had%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-american-income-life-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Department%20of%20Justice%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20two%20short-sellers%20released%20damning%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobe%20Life%20Inc.%2C%20a%20publicly%20traded%20insurance%20company%20based%20in%20Texas%2C%20was%20once%20flying%20high.%20Its%20top%20insurance%20agents%20basked%20in%20luxury%20with%20lavish%20company%20retreats%20and%20expensive%20sports%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20holding%20company%20operates%20five%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiaries%2C%20the%20largest%20of%20which%20is%20American%20Income%20Life%2C%20or%20AIL.%20Driving%20AIL's%20profits%20is%20a%20layer%20of%20affiliated%20insurance%20agencies%20that%20exclusively%20sell%20AIL%20policies.%20Arias%20Organization%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Arias%20Agencies%2C%20has%20historically%20been%20one%20of%20AIL's%20biggest%20producers%3B%20it%20is%20captained%20by%20Simon%20Arias%20III%2C%20who%20multiple%20former%20agents%20said%20has%20built%20an%20aggressive%2C%20drug-fueled%20sales%20culture%20that%20recalls%20the%20Wolf%20of%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20foundation%20began%20to%20crumble%20when%20a%20former%20Arias%20agent%20named%20Renee%20Zinsky%20filed%20a%20stunning%20federal%20lawsuit%20in%202022%2C%20alleging%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epervasive%20culture%20of%20sexual%20assault%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20customer%20abuses%20at%20Arias.%20She%20accused%20her%20manager%2C%20senior%20leader%20Mike%20Russin%2C%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20her%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20was%20the%20first%20outlet%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20on%20Zinsky's%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20BI's%20investigation%20also%20cited%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20former%20agents%20who%20described%20a%20toxic%20workplace%20that%20was%20punitive%20to%20agents%20who%20didn't%20reach%20their%20goals%2C%20alleging%20that%20they%20were%20encouraged%20to%20put%20through%20charges%20without%20customer%20approval%20and%20write%20policies%20for%20dead%20people%20to%20drum%20up%20commissions.%20After%20BI's%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20appeared%2C%20multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-fallout-after-allegations-of-sexual-assault-arias-agency-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20agents%20came%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sexual%20assault%20accusations%20and%20accounts%20of%20brutal%20hazing%20and%20customer%20abuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20then%20really%20began%20to%20fall%20apart%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20August%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-arias-under-investigation-after-allegations-of-fraud-sexual-abuse-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20had%20dumped%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20half%20of%20its%206.35%20million%20shares%20of%20Globe%20Life.%20That%20same%20month%2C%20an%20Arias%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20that%20insurance%20regulators%20had%20shown%20up%20for%20an%20unannounced%20visit%20at%20Arias%20headquarters%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20asking%20to%20speak%20with%20Simon%20Arias.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Pennsylvania%20insurance%20regulators%20issued%20AIL%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insurance.pa.gov%2FRegulations%2FRegulatory%2520Actions%2FDocuments%2FCurrent%2520Market%2520Conduct%2FFinal%2520Exam%2520Report-%2520American%2520Income%2520Life.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%24130%2C000%20fine%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20deceptive%20consumer%20practices.%20Though%20Arias%20Organization%20was%20not%20named%20specifically%2C%20it%20operates%20half%20of%20AIL's%20offices%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20move%20in%20November%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-takes-up-sexual-harassment-cases-against-globe-life-subsidiary-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEqual%20Employment%20Opportunity%20Commission%20reversed%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20prior%20dismissal%20of%20two%20sexual%20harassment%20claims%20against%20AIL%20and%20the%20Arias%20Organization%2C%20including%20Zinsky's%20claim%20and%20one%20by%20another%20former%20agent%2C%20Abeni%20Mayfield%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-arias-under-investigation-after-allegations-of-fraud-sexual-abuse-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhose%20allegations%20BI%20had%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Three%20current%20or%20former%20insurance%20agents%20filed%20new%20charges%20with%20the%20EEOC%2C%20accusing%20the%20Arias%20Organization%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20racism%2C%20and%20customer%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20BI%20broke%20the%20news%20that%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-amer