dents%20think%20is%20so%20ugly%20they%20are%20making%20diss%20tracks%20about%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Detroit's%20new%20sign%20attracted%20controversy%20after%20being%20billed%20as%20%26quot%3BHollywood-like.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661c0ae73f923f7dab07c469%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22759%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDetroit's%20new%20sign%20attracted%20controversy%20after%20being%20billed%20as%20%26quot%3BHollywood-like.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECity%20of%20Detroit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDetroit%20spent%20%24400%2C000%20on%20a%20new%20Hollywood-style%20sign%20as%20it%20hosts%20the%20NFL%20Draft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDetroit%20views%20the%20NFL%20Draft%20as%20a%20chance%20to%20showcase%20its%20recovery%20after%20years%20of%20financial%20trouble.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResidents%20have%20widely%20mocked%20the%20sign%20and%20at%20least%20one%20rapper%20made%20it%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20diss%20track.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20want%20to%20know%20is%20now%20much%20we%20paid%20for%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Detroit%20rapper%20Gmac%20Cash%20asks%20in%20his%20new%20single%2C%20%26quot%3BDetroit%20Sign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%3A%20About%20%24400%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Parker%2C%20the%20city's%20deputy%20chief%20operations%20officer%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freep.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fmichigan%2Fwayne%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fdetroit-hollywood-sign-nfl-draft-2024%2F72543148007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Detroit%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20sign%20is%20one%20of%20several%20infrastructure%20improvements%20planned%20ahead%20of%20the%20NFL%20Draft%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Detroit%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20city%20installed%20the%20sign%2C%20Parker%20told%20the%20outlet%20it%20would%20look%20%26quot%3Blike%20the%20Hollywood%20sign%2C%20but%20smaller.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECash%20disagrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20our%20sign%20was%20going%20to%20look%20like%20Hollywood%2C%26quot%3B%20Cash%20raps.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20probably%20why%20they%20put%20this%20bitch%20right%20by%20the%20hood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECash's%20new%20song%20%E2%80%94%20in%20which%20he%20says%20the%20sign%20looks%20like%20%26quot%3BTimes%20New%20Roman%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20attracted%20more%20than%201%20million%20views%20on%20TikTok%20in%20just%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECash%2C%20a%20local%20Detroit%20rapper%2C%20has%20several%20songs%20about%20landmark%20attractions%20in%20the%20city%2C%20usually%20with%20a%20comedic%20spin.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20performed%20his%20song%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvSqB4smII4I%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGiant%20Slide%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20Jimmy%20Kimmel%20Live%20after%20the%20city's%20giant%20metal%20slide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F08%2F26%2Fus%2Fbelle-isle-giant-slide-detroit.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebriefly%20closed%20following%20safety%20complaints%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20new%20slide%20you%20got%20to%20take%20a%20Tylenol%20to%20get%20on.%20If%20your%20kids%20gettin'%20on%20your%20nerves%2C%20make%20em%20get%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20raps%20in%20the%20song's%20chorus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParker%20said%20the%20city%20spent%20%24400%2C000%20of%20city%20funds%20to%20pay%20Fairmount%20Sign%20Company%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20Detroit%2C%20for%20the%20sign%2C%20the%20Free%20Press%20reported.%20The%20sign's%20letters%20stand%20at%20eight%20feet%20tall%20and%20sit%20on%20two-foot%20concrete%20blocks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fp%2FsnTWygxut2AERQ8p%2F%3Fmibextid%3DWC7FNe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%