Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20was%20hit%20for%20three%20consecutive%20sixes%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20match%20against%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20on%20Sunday.%20Hardik%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20MI%20bowlers%20with%20two%20wickets%20but%20he%20was%20slammed%20for%2020%20runs%20by%20Dhoni%20in%20the%20final%20four%20balls%20of%20the%20CSK%20innings.%20Gavaskar%20slammed%20Hardik%20for%20his%20'ordinary%20bowling%20and%20ordinary%20captaincy'%20and%20criticised%20the%20kind%20of%20deliveries%20that%20he%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProbably%20the%20worst%20kind%20of%20bowling%20that%20I've%20seen%20for%20a%20long%2C%20long%20time.%20It%20almost%20looks%20like%20I've%20had%20this%20embrace%20with%20my%20hero.%20I've%20got%20a%20bowling%20kind%20of%20deliveries%20that%20he's%20gonna%20hit%20for%20sixes.%20One%206%20is%20fine.%20The%20next%20one%20again%20a%20length%20ball%20when%20you%20know%20that%20this%20batter%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20length%20ball%20to%20hit.%20The%20third%20ball%20again%2C%20a%20full%20toss%20on%20the%20leg%20side%20and%20he's%20looking%20for%20it%20and%20hits%20it%20for%20a%206.%20Absolutely%20ordinary%20bowling%2C%20ordinary%20captaincy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20during%20his%20analysis%20in%20the%20mid-innings%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20interaction%20that%20Hardik%20and%20Dhoni%20had%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20match.%20Hardik%20ran%20to%20Dhoni%20and%20hugged%20the%20former%20India%20skipper%20in%20a%20moment%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20century%20went%20in%20vain%20as%20Mumbai%20Indians%20lost%20to%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20by%2020%20runs.%20Rohit%20played%20a%20brilliant%20knock%20but%20the%20hosts%20kept%20losing%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%20and%20an%20impressive%20four-wicket%20haul%20from%C2%A0Matheesha%20Pathirana%20ensured%20the%20victory%20for%20CSK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20slammed%20half-centuries%20while%20Dhoni%20provided%20a%20late%20flourish%20against%20Hardik's%20bowling%20to%20take%20CSK's%20total%20to%20206.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20victory%2C%20CSK%20remain%20in%20the%20third%20position%20while%20Mumbai%20Indians%20are%20eighth%20in%20the%20competition%20with%20just%20four%20points%20from%20six%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713117720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnjeo7lg_s_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fworst-kind-of-bowling-sunil-gavaskar-blasts-hardik-pandya-after-ms-dhonis-fiery-knock-5442011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20was%20furious%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20Hardik%20Pandya%20after%20he%20was%20hit%20for%20three%20consecutive%20sixes%20by%20MS%20Dhoni%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%202024%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Century%20In%20Vain%20As%20CSK%20Beat%20MI%20By%2020%20Runs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMI%20vs%20CSK%20Highlights%2C%20IPL%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sri%20Lankan%20pacer%20Matheesha%20Pathirana%20came%20up%20with%20his%20best%20IPL%20figures%2C%20grabbing%20four%20wickets%20as%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20defeated%20Mumbai%20Indians%20by%2020%20runs%2C%20despite%20a%20heroic%20unbeaten%20century%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%20Pathirana%20took%20the%20wickets%20of%20Ishan%20