ke%20part%20in%20a%20counter-offensive%20against%20Iran%20if%20Israel%20decides%20to%20retaliate%20for%20a%20mass%20drone%20and%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20territory%20overnight%2C%20a%20White%20House%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20of%20open%20warfare%20erupting%20between%20the%20arch%20Middle%20East%20foes%20and%20dragging%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20put%20the%20region%20on%20edge%2C%20triggering%20calls%20for%20restraint%20from%20global%20powers%20and%20Arab%20nations%20to%20avoid%20further%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20media%20reported%20earlier%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Biden%20had%20informed%20Netanyahu%20he%20would%20not%20participate%20in%20retaliatory%20action%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20overnight.%20The%20remarks%20were%20confirmed%20to%20Reuters%20by%20a%20White%20House%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20will%20continue%20to%20help%20Israel%20defend%20itself%2C%20but%20does%20not%20want%20war%2C%20John%20Kirby%2C%20the%20White%20House's%20top%20national%20security%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20ABC's%20%26quot%3BThis%20Week%26quot%3B%20program%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20launched%20the%20attack%20over%20a%20suspected%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20its%20consulate%20in%20Syria%20on%20April%201%20that%20killed%20top%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20commanders%20and%20followed%20months%20of%20clashes%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran's%20regional%20allies%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20attack%20from%20more%20than%20300%20missiles%20and%20drones%2C%20mostly%20launched%20from%20inside%20Iran%2C%20caused%20only%20modest%20damage%20in%20Israel%20as%20most%20were%20shot%20down%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20US%2C%20Britain%20and%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Air%20Force%20base%20in%20southern%20Israel%20was%20hit%2C%20but%20continued%20to%20operate%20as%20normal%20and%20a%207-year%20old%20child%20was%20seriously%20hurt%20by%20shrapnel.%20There%20were%20no%20other%20reports%20of%20serious%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20senior%20Israeli%20ministers%20signalled%20on%20Sunday%20that%20retaliation%20by%20Israel%20is%20not%20imminent%20and%20it%20would%20not%20act%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20build%20a%20regional%20coalition%20and%20exact%20the%20price%20from%20Iran%20in%20the%20fashion%20and%20timing%20that%20is%20right%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20centrist%20minister%20Benny%20Gantz%20said%20ahead%20of%20a%20war%20cabinet%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20also%20said%20Israel%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20form%20a%20strategic%20alliance%20against%20%26quot%3Bthis%20grave%20threat%20by%20Iran%20which%20is%20threatening%20to%20mount%20nuclear%20explosives%20on%20these%20missiles%2C%20which%20could%20be%20an%20extremely%20grave%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Iran%20denies%20seeking%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20Army%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Major%20General%20Mohammad%20Bagheri%20warned%20on%20television%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20response%20will%20be%20much%20larger%20than%20tonight's%20military%20action%20if%20Israel%20retaliates%20against%20Iran%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20Washington%20its%20bases%20could%20also%20be%20attacked%20if%20it%20helped%20Israel%20retaliate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Amir%20Abdollahian%20said%20Tehran%20had%20informed%20the%20United%20States%20its%20attack%20on%20Israel%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Blimited%26quot%3B%20and%20for%20self%20defence%20and%20that%20regional%20neighbours%20had%20also%20been%20informed%20of%20its%20planned%20strikes%2072%20hours%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Turkish%20diplomatic%20source%20said%20Iran%20had%20informed%20Turkey%20in%20advance%20of%20what%20would%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20said%20the%20attack%20was%20aimed%20at%20punishing%20%26quot%3BIsraeli%20crimes%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20now%20%26quot%3Bdeemed%20the%20matter%20concluded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20China%2C%20France%20and%20Germany%20as%20well%20as%20Arab%20states%20Egypt%2C%20Qatar%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20urged%20restraint%20and%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20was%20set%20to%20meet%20at%204%20p.m.%20ET%20(2000%20GMT)%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20stop%20a%20further%20escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20said%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20China.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20only%20warn%20everyone%2C%20especially%20Iran%2C%20against%20continuing%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkey%20also%20warned%20Iran%20it%20did%20not%20want%20further%20tension%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EESCALATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20debated%20how%20far%20Iran's%20attack%20was%20calibrated%20to%20cause%20genuine%20devastation%20in%20Israel%2C%20or%20to%20save%20face%20at%20home%20after%20vows%20of%20revenge%20while%20avoiding%20a%20major%20new%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Iranians%20took%20into%20consideration%20the%20fact%20that%20Israel%20has%20a%20very%2C%20very%20strong%20multi-layer%20anti-missile%20system%20and%20they%20probably%20took%20into%20consideration%20that%20there%20will%20not%20be%20too%20many%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sima%20Shine%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20Mossad%20official%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20National%20Security%20Studies%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20Iran%20was%20hoping%20for%20a%20muted%20response%2C%20like%20with%20its%20missile%20attacks%20on%20U.S.%20forces%20in%20Iraq%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20Guards%20commander%20Qassem%20Soleimani%20in%202020%2C%20she%20warned%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Israel%20sees%20it%20this%20way%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%20Iran's%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20seized%20an%20Israel-linked%20cargo%20ship%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20energy%20shipping%20routes%2C%20underscoring%20the%20risks%20to%20the%20world%20economy%20of%20a%20wider%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20flights%20were%20suspended%20in%20countries%20across%20the%20region%20and%20share%20prices%20fell%20in%20stock%20markets%20in%20Israel%20and%20Gulf%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20Israel%20invaded%20after%20an%20attack%20by%20Iran-backed%20Hamas%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20has%20spread%20to%20fronts%20with%20Iran-aligned%20groups%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%2C%20Yemen%20and%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20most%20powerful%20ally%20in%20the%20region%2C%20the%20Lebanese%20Shi'ite%20group%20Hezbollah%20fired%20rockets%20at%20an%20Israeli%20base%20overnight.%20Israel%20said%20it%20struck%20a%20Hezbollah%20site%20deep%20inside%20Lebanon%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYemen's%20Houthis%2C%20who%20have%20been%20firing%20missiles%20at%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20what%20they%20say%20is%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20called%20Iran's%20attack%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Oct.%207%20attack%20in%20which%20Israel%20says%201%2C200%20were%20killed%20and%20253%20taken%20hostage%2C%20along%20with%20internal%20discontent%20with%20the%20government%20and%20international%20pressure%20over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%2C%20form%20the%20backdrop%20to%20Netanyahu's%20decisions%20over%20a%20response.%20At%20least%2033%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20Israel%20began%20its%20military%20offensive%2C%20according%20to%20authorities%20in%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20has%20for%20years%20advocated%20a%20tough%20military%20line%20against%20Iran%2C%20pushing%20the%20United%20States%20for%20harder%20action%20over%20Tehran's%20nuclear%20programme%20and%20its%20backing%20for%20Hezbollah%2C%20Hamas%20and%20other%20groups%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20although%20there%20was%20alarm%20at%20the%20first%20direct%20attack%20from%20another%20country%20in%20more%20than%20three%20decades%2C%20the%20mood%20was%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20trauma%20after%20the%20Hamas-led%20attack%20on%20Oct.7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we've%20been%20given%20license%20to%20respond%20now.%20I%20mean%20it%20was%20a%20major%20attack%20from%20Iran...%20I%20imagine%20Israel%20will%20respond%20and%20may%20be%20over%20quickly%20and%20get%20back%20to%20normal%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeremy%20Smith%2C%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Iran%2C%20state%20television%20showed%20small%20gatherings%20in%20several%20cities%20celebrating%20the%20attack%2C%20but%20in%20private%20some%20Iranians%20were%20worried%20about%20Israel's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIran%20gave%20Netanyahu%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20attack%20our%20country.%20But%20we%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Iran%2C%20will%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20this%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shima%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20nurse%2C%20from%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713109980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fdh45inf8_joe-biden-netanyahu_625x300_27_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-conflict-joe-biden-tells-benjamin-netanyahu-us-would-not-take-part-in-israeli-counter-offensive-against-iran-report-5441051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20told%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20that%20the%20United%20States%20would%20not%20participate%20in%20any%20Israeli%20counter-offensive%20against%20Iran%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20on%20Sunday%20by%20CNN%20and%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-conflict-joe-biden-tells-benjamin-netanyahu-us-would-not-take-part-in-israeli-counter-offensive-against-iran-report-5441051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-conflict-joe-biden-tells-benjamin-netanyahu-us-would-not-take-part-in-israeli-counter-offensive-against-iran-report-5441051%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-conflict-joe-biden-tells-benjamin-netanyahu-us-would-not-take-part-in-israeli-counter-offensive-against-iran-report-5441051%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Scientists%20Design%20Material%20That%20Removes%20Microplastics%20From%20Water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrom%20oceans%20to%20mountains%2C%20microplastics%20have%20been%20found%20almost%20everywhere%20on%20the%20planet.%20According%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Development%20Programme%20(UNDP)%2C%20these%20tiny%20particles%20of%20plastic%20less%20than%205%20millimetres%20in%20size%2C%20have%20infiltrated%20our%20oceans%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20even%20the%20air%20we%20breathe.%20These%20tiny%20debris%20can%20enter%20our%20bodies%20through%20the%20water%20we%20drink%20and%C2%A0pose%20a%20massive%20threat%20to%20our%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20combat%20the%20menace%20of%20plastic%20pollution%2C%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%C2%A0have%20designed%20a%20sustainable%20hydrogel%20to%20remove%20microplastics%20from%20water.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiisc.ac.in%2Fevents%2Fnovel-hydrogel-removes-microplastics-from-water%2F%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0Bengaluru-based%20IISc%20explained%20that%20the%20hydrogel%20has%20a%20unique%20intertwined%20polymer%20network%20that%20can%20bind%20the%20contaminants%20and%20degrade%20them%20using%20UV%20light%20irradiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20scientists%20have%20tried%20using%20filtering%20membranes%20to%20remove%20microplastics%2C%20however%2C%20the%20membranes%20can%20become%20clogged%20with%20these%20tiny%20particles%2C%20rendering%20them%20unsustainable.%20The%20IISc%20team%20led%20by%20Suryasarathi%20Bose%2C%20a%20Professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Materials%20Engineering%2C%20then%20turned%20to%203D%20hydrogels%C2%A0for%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20novel%20hydrogel%20developed%20by%20the%20team%20consists%20of%20three%20different%20polymer%20layers%20%E2%80%93%20chitosan%2C%20polyvinyl%20alcohol%20and%20polyaniline%20%E2%80%93%20intertwined%20together%2C%20making%20an%20Interpenetrating%20Polymer%20Network%20(IPN)%20architecture.%20The%20team%20infused%20this%20matrix%20with%20nanoclusters%20of%20a%20material%20called%20copper%20substitute%20polyoxometalate%20(Cu-POM).%20These%20nanoclusters%20are%20catalysts%20that%20can%20use%20UV%20light%20to%20degrade%20the%20microplastics.%20The%20combination%20of%20the%20polymers%20and%20nanoclusters%20resulted%20in%20a%20strong%20hydrogel%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20adsorb%20and%20degrade%20large%20amounts%20of%20microplastics%2C''%20the%20press%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20crushed%20food%20container%20lids%20and%20other%20daily-use%20plastic%20products%20to%20create%20two%20of%20the%20most%20common%20microplastics%20existing%20in%20nature%3A%20polyvinyl%20chloride%20and%20polypropylene.%20They%20also%20added%20a%20fluorescent%20dye%20to%20the%20microplastics%20to%20track%20how%20much%20was%20being%20adsorbed%20and%20degraded%20by%20the%20hydrogel%20under%20different%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20hydrogel%20was%20found%20to%20be%20highly%20efficient%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20remove%20about%2095%25%20and%2093%25%20of%20the%20two%20different%20types%20of%20microplastics%20in%20water%20at%20near-neutral%20pH%20(%E2%88%BC6.5)%2C''%20Mr%20Bose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20hydrogel%20has%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20its%20usefulness%2C%20it%20can%20be%20repurposed%20into%20carbon%20nanomaterials%20capable%20of%20removing%20heavy%20metals%C2%A0from%20polluted%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20now%20plan%20to%20develop%20a%20device%20that%20can%20be%20deployed%20on%20a%20large%20scale%20to%20help%20clean%20up%20microplastics%20from%20various%20water%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713109500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkpe9ov48_hydrogel_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fiisc-researchers-design-sustainable-hydrogel-to-remove-microplastics-from-water-5441401%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Microplastics%20are%20tiny%20plastic%20debris%20that%20can%20enter%20our%20bodies%20through%20the%20water%20we%20drink%20and%20expose%20us%20to%20illnesses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fiisc-researchers-design-sustainable-hydrogel-to-remove-microplastics-from-water-5441401%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fiisc-researchers-design-sustainable-hydrogel-to-remove-microplastics-from-water-5441401%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fiisc-researchers-design-sustainable-hydrogel-to-remove-microplastics-from-water-5441401%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20the%20'hero'%20police%20officer%20who%20stopped%20Sydney%20attacker%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713108720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F04%2F768x432%2Fskynews-amy-scott-nsw-police_6521659.jpg%3F20240414214116%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famy-scott-who-is-the-hero-police-officer-who-single-handedly-stopped-sydney-attacker-joel-cauchi-13115403%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20knife-wielding%20man%20went%20on%20a%20stabbing%20spree%20in%20Sydney's%20biggest%20mall%2C%20one%20lone%20of