3052834%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20post%20ignited%20a%20debate%20on%20social%20media%20and%20garnered%20a%20variety%20of%20responses.%20A%20majority%20of%20users%20agreed%20that%20such%20an%20intense%C2%A0study%20routine%20of%2018%2B%20hours%20doesn't%20make%20any%20sense%20and%20that%20quality%20matters%20more%20than%20quantity.%20Many%20also%20slammed%20such%20vloggers%20for%20confusing%20aspirants%20and%20thanked%20Mr%20Sharan%20for%20pointing%20out%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Sir%20I%20recently%20watched%20one%20of%20these%20vlog.%20They%20are%20misleading%20us%20and%20they%20are%20not%20giving%20correct%20information%20about%20the%20related%20exams.%20Thank%20you%20sir%20for%20raising%20this%20type%20of%20issue.%20Secondly%2C%20it's%20not%20about%20how%20many%20hours%20one%20studies%2C%20it's%20about%20how%20much%20one%20can%20retain%20and%20reproduce%2C%20One%20will%20not%20get%20marks%20for%20the%20No%20of%20hours%20one%20has%20studied%20but%20what%20one%20has%20written%20in%20one's%20answer%20sheet.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''I'm%20thinking%20who's%20watching%20this%3F%20They%20just%20create%20unnecessary%20FOMO%20it's%20a%20new%20way%20to%20earn%20money.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20''That's%20what%20UPSC%20also%20wants%20from%20the%20Aspirants%2C%20Quality%20not%20the%20Quantity!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Hope%20the%20aspirants%20understand%20that%20it's%20the%20productivity%20that%20matters%2C%20not%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20that%20you%20spend%20in%20front%20of%20the%20books.%20%C2%A0And%20on%20top%20of%20that%20each%20one%20of%20them%20should%20understand%20their%20capabilities%20and%20try%20not%20to%20copy%20others.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fifth%20said%2C%20''Thank%20you%20so%20much%40AwanishSharan%20sir%20for%20raising%20this%20kind%20of%20misleading%20blogs%20and%20other%2