tel-aviv-flights-amid-escalating-conflict-124041400455_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-temporarily-suspends-tel-aviv-flights-amid-escalating-conflict-124041400455_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-temporarily-suspends-tel-aviv-flights-amid-escalating-conflict-124041400455_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20End%20Of%20Opium%20Poppy%20Cultivation%20In%20Manipur%20Soon%3F%20Data%20Shows...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20area%20of%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20in%20violence-hit%20Manipur%20has%20declined%2060%20per%20cent%20since%202021%2C%20latest%20data%20from%20the%20autonomous%20government%20institution%20Manipur%20Remote%20Sensing%20Applications%20Centre%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scientific%20institution%20under%20the%20planning%20department%20whose%20key%20work%20is%20to%20visualise%20geographic%20data%20had%20been%20mapping%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20across%20Manipur%20between%20September%202021%20and%20January%202024%2C%20during%20the%20poppy-sowing%20and%20-harvesting%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20used%20satellite%20imagery%20technology%20from%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation's%20(ISRO)%20Hyderabad-based%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Landsat%20programme%20run%20jointly%20by%20the%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration%20(NASA)%20and%20the%20United%20States%20Geological%20Survey%20(USGS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20satellite%20imagery-based%20report%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Remote%20Sensing%20Applications%20Centre%20(MARSAC)%20shows%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20area%20fell%2040%20per%20cent%20from%2028%2C599%20acres%20in%202021-22%20to%2016%2C890%20acres%20in%202022-23.%20The%20area%20shrunk%20further%20by%2032%20per%20cent%20to%2011%2C288%20acres%20in%202023-24%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20In%20total%2C%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20area%20in%20Manipur%20fell%2060%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20three-year%20crop%20cycle%20period%20between%202021%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARSAC%20submitted%20the%20report%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%20in%20early%20March%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20report%20gave%20an%20empirical%20evidence%20to%20measure%20the%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20drugs%26quot%3B%20campaign%20of%20the%20state%20BJP%20government%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20they%20said.%20Mr%20Singh%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202017%2C%20and%20won%20a%20second%20term%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnmdcs0po_marsac_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20factored%20in%2019%2C135%20acres%20of%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20destroyed%20between%202017%20and%202024%2C%20MARSAC%20said%20in%20the%20document%20titled%20'Mapping%20and%20Estimation%20of%20Opium%20Poppy%20Cultivation%20Area%20in%20Manipur'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARSAC%20did%20not%20give%20a%20break-up%2C%20however%2C%20of%20what%20factors%20could%20have%20led%20to%20a%20shrinking%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20area%20in%20Manipur.%20Senior%20officers%20in%20the%20forest%20department%2C%20and%20the%20Narcotics%20and%20Affairs%20of%20Border%20(NAB)%20indicated%20the%20sustained%20drive%20to%20stop%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20in%20the%20past%20seven%20years%20definitely%20had%20an%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERemote%20Sensing%20Data%2C%20Ground%20Verification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARSAC%20said%20the%20best%20season%20to%20plant%20and%20harvest%20opium%20poppy%20is%20from%20September%20to%20February.%20Sometimes%2C%20the%20harvest%20extends%20till%20March-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20usually%20acquire%20the%20LISS-IV%20satellite%20imagery%20from%20ISRO's%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20for%20first%20week%20of%20September%2C%20second%20week%20of%20October%2C%20first%20week%20of%20December%2C%20and%20second%20week%20of%20February%2C%26quot%3B%20MARSAC%20said%20in%20the%20report%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20home-grown%20high-resolution%20camera%20LISS-IV%20-%20launched%20onboard%20the%20Resourcesat-1%20satellite%20by%20ISRO%20in%202003%20-%20to%20gather%20data%20on%20vegetation%2C%20landforms%2C%20and%20geological%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20clouds%20blocking%20the%20ground%20in%20some%20seasons%2C%20MARSAC%20had%20to%20use%20the%20multispectral%20instrument%20Sentinel-2A%20of%20the%20European%20Union%20Space%20Programme%2C%20and%20the%20US'%20Landsat%207%20satellite%20to%20map%20poppy%20plantations.%20Multispectral%20imaging%20(MSI)%20uses%20different%20wavelength%20bands%20to%20capture%20data%2C%20and%20by%20looking%20for%20spectral%20absorption%20or%20emission%20of%20different%20material%2C%20MSI%20can%20identify%20vegetation%20and%20check%20crop%20yield.%C2%A0Poppy%20plants%20will%20have%20different%20spectral%20signatures%20at%20different%20stages%20of%20their%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20next%20step%2C%20forest%20department%20and%20NAB%20personnel%20went%20to%20the%20areas%20where%20satellite%20imagery%20indicated%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20to%20verify%20the%20data.%20If%20confirmed%2C%20they%20recorded%20the%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20(GPS)%20coordinates%20of%20these%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20Of%20The%20Districts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20survey%20from%20September%202021%20sowing%20to%20the%20February%202022%20harvest%20seasons%2C%20MARSAC%20found%20111%20poppy%20cultivation%20clusters%20in%20eight%20out%20of%20Manipur's%2016%20districts%20-%20or%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20districts%20in%20Manipur%20grew%20opium%20poppy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F0ev8m39g_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKangpokpi%20-%20the%20long%2C%20inverted%20U-shaped%20district%20that%20surrounds%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20valley%20from%20the%20north%20-%20had%20the%20largest%20area%20under%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20at%209%2C518%20acres%2C%20followed%20by%20Churachandpur%20in%20the%20south%20at%206%2C688%20acres.%20Tamenglong%20had%20the%20least%20at%20668%20acres.%20Ukhrul%20had%201%2C931%20acres%20of%20poppy%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffg7evod_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022-23%20survey%20found%20203%20poppy%20cultivation%20clusters%20in%20nine%20out%20of%20the%2016%20districts.%20The%20poppy%20cultivation%20area%20in%20Kangpokpi%20fell%2043%20per%20cent%20to%205%2C407%20acres%2C%20and%20in%20Churachandpur%20it%20shrunk%2039%20per%20cent%20to%204%2C063%20acres.%20Tamenglong's%20poppy%20cultivation%20area%20also%20shrunk%20by%20a%20massive%2085%20per%20cent%20to%20only%2096%20acres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARSAC%20didn't%20find%20opium%20poppy%20fields%20in%20Noney%20district%20in%202021-22%3B%20however%2C%20the%20remote%20sensing%20agency%20detected%20132%20acres%20in%20Noney%20in%202022-23.%20Ukhrul%20had%201%2C729%20acres%20of%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjf2121dg_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20from%20September%202023%20to%20January%202024%20detected%20141%20clusters%20in%20nine%20districts.%20Though%20Kangpokpi%20still%20had%20the%20largest%20opium%20cultivation%20at%204%2C321%20acres%2C%20the%20growing%20area%20fell%2020%20per%20cent%20since%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenapati%20replaced%20Churachandpur%20as%20the%20district%20with%20the%20second-largest%20opium%20cultivation%20area%20at%202%2C333%20acres.%20Ukrhul%20had%201%2C598%20acres%20while%20Churachandpur%20had%201%2C488%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ftl93iu58_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgrrcd9a_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5eqmv0og_marsac-data_625x300_14_April_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20between%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%2C%20who%20are%20the%20dominant%20population%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20a%20few%20other%20areas%2C%20and%20the%20Meitei%20community%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20central%20Manipur's%20valley%20areas%20including%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20has%20led%20to%20heightened%20enforcement%20action%20in%20remote%20locations%20near%20the%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20that%20are%20used%20by%20drug-traffickers%20to%20transport%20opium%20poppy%20to%20processing%20plants%2C%20NAB%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShrinking%20Poppy%20Cultivation%20Areas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20sources%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bwar%20on%20drugs%26quot%3B%20campaign%20that%20began%20in%20June%202018%20has%20led%20to%20a%20gradual%20fall%20in%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation.%20They%20said%20if%20the%20current%20rate%20of%20decline%20continues%20for%20four-five%20consecutive%20crop%20cycles%2C%20and%20strict%20enforcement%20becomes%20the%20rule%2C%20there%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20left%20to%20feed%20the%20processing%20units%20for%20making%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20its%20last%20session%2C%20it%20was%20mentioned%20that%201%2C889%20acres%20of%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20were%20destroyed%20in%20the%20four-year%20period%20from%202013%20to%202016.%20In%20comparison%2C%2011%2C438%20acres%20of%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20were%20destroyed%20during%20the%20four-year%20period%20from%202017%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARSAC%20said%20finding%20the%20location%20of%20poppy%20fields%20and%20mapping%20their%20spatial%20distribution%20help%20the%20government%20run%20eradication%20plans%20with%20a%20high%20success%20rate%2C%20and%20destroy%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20the%20narcotics%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20shifting%20cultivation%20pattern%2C%20poppy-growing%20fields%20were%20observed%20repeatedly%20in%20the%20same%20area%2C%20and%20usually%20found%20very%20far%20away%20from%20village%20settlements%2C%26quot%3B%20MARSAC%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fe033b7ho_poppy-generic-manipur_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20mentioned%20in%20the%20report's%20summary%20a%20most%20controversial%20aspect%20of%20this%20issue%20-%20%26quot%3Bdeforestation%20due%20to%20mass%20poppy%20cultivation%20has%20led%20to%20adverse%20impacts%20on%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20including%20soil%20erosion%2C%20loss%20of%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20changes%20in%20the%20local%20climate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20no%20study%20on%20the%20effect%20that%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20in%20Manipur%20may%20have%20on%20natural%20systems%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20an%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%20posted%20in%20the%20border%20state%20told%20NDTV%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20on%20a%20comprehensive%20survey%20into%20this%20issue.%20No%20such%20survey%20has%20been%20done%20yet%20in%20Manipur.%20There%20are%20studies%20in%20other%20nations%2C%20but%20we%20can't%20compare%20the%20data%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20key%20parameters.%20Maybe%20the%20unchecked%20use%20of%20banned%20pesticides%20in%20remote%20poppy%20farms%20is%20one%20area%20which%20will%20have%20the%20same%20effect%20on%20natural%20systems%2C%20whether%20in%20Manipur%20or%20Colombia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20told%20NDTV%20on%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20who%20regularly%20visited%20villages%20along%20the%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20told%20NDTV%20that%20soil%20erosion%20due%20to%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20may%20be%20high%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20exposure%20of%20the%20hard%20shale%20underneath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20shifting%20cultivation%2C%20poppy%20farming%20is%20a%20continuous%20process%20throughout%20the%20year%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20high%20soil%20erosion.%20Most%20of%20the%20rivers%20are%20drying%20up%20in%20winter.%20The%20hills%20cleared%20of%20forests%20to%20grow%20poppy%20can%20no%20longer%20store%20water%20during%20monsoon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20retired%20officer%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20a%20drought-like%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20water%20bodies%20drying%20up%20frequently%20due%20to%20mass%20deforestation%2C%20forest%20officers%20have%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGPS%20Coordinates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MARSAC%20report%20includes%20455%20GPS%20coordinates%20of%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20NAB%20and%20forest%20department%20officers%20found%20opium%20poppy%20cultivation%20during%20the%20three-year%20survey.%20Some%20coordinates%20are%20of%20the%20same%20locations%20every%20year%20as%20LISS-IV%2C%20Sentinel%202A%20and%20Landsat%207%20detected%20repeat%20cropping%20on%20the%20same%20plots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20accessed%20the%20coordinates%20and%20checked%20250%20areas%20in%20random.%20Some%20poppy%20fields%20are%20just%205%20km%20away%20from%20big%20settlements%2C%20and%20others%20are%20deep%20in%20the%20hills%20with%20no%20road%20leading%20to%20them.%20Some%20are%20also%20only%20a%20few%20100%20metres%20away%20from%20walled%2C%20circular%20settlements%20with%20uniformly%20sized%20huts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20acquisition%20dates%20and%20the%20satellites%20used%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Image%20acquisition%20dates%20and%20the%20satellites%20used%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhrrfbeh8_satellite_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImage%20acquisition%20dates%20and%20the%20satellites%20used%20-%202021-22%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20acquisition%20dates%20and%20the%20satellites%20used%20-%202022-23%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Image%20acquisition%20dates%20and%20the%20satellites%20used%20-%202022-23%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%