p%3EUkhrul%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Kamjong%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Kamjong%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fsqck8mg_kamjong_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamjong%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Churachandpur%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Churachandpur%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5s058bn_churachandpur-poppy_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurachandpur%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandel%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Chandel%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fpvq69808_chandel-poppy_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandel%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Grow%20Opium%20Poppy%20For%20Narcotics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20retired%20IAS%20officer%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20the%20number%20one%20reason%20why%20farmers%20grow%20poppy%20in%20the%20hill%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoor%20farmers%20in%20the%20hills%20face%20severe%20difficulties%20in%20growing%20regular%20crops%20and%20the%20returns%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20studies%20have%20shown.%20There%20have%20been%20cases%20when%2C%20after%20facing%20regular%20crop%20loss%20year%20after%20year%2C%20farmers%20had%20to%20move%20to%20poppy%20cultivation%20as%20it%20fetches%20attractive%20prices%20and%20the%20poppy%20growing%20cycle%20is%20relatively%20shorter%20and%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20has%20been%20running%20schemes%20to%20help%20farmers%20switch%20from%20growing%20poppy%20to%20other%20crops.%20But%20reports%20indicate%20the%20schemes%20have%20not%20been%20effective.%20%26quot%3BSome%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20find%20out%20alternatives%2C%20but%20on-ground%20implementation%20is%20very%20limited.%20The%20horticulture%20department%20has%20been%20providing%20vegetable%20seeds%2C%20but%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20monitoring%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20against%20opium%20poppy%20production%20in%20Manipur%20can%20be%20won%20only%20if%20economically%20viable%20alternatives%20are%20provided%20to%20farmers%2C%20who%20are%20excluded%20from%20development%20initiatives%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology-Guwahati%20professor%20Ngamjahao%20Kipgen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fengage%2Farticle%2Fwhy-are-farmers-manipur-cultivating-poppy%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Political%20Weekly%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20November%202019%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Manipur%20government's%20war%20on%20drugs%20campaign%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Police%20and%20anti-narcotics%20personnel%20destroy%20opium%20poppy%20plants%20at%20Kholen%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20December%202%2C%202023.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Police%20and%20anti-narcotics%20personnel%20destroy%20opium%20poppy%20plants%20at%20Kholen%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20December%202%2C%202023.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhob376ug_poppy-generic_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20and%20anti-narcotics%20personnel%20destroy%20opium%20poppy%20plants%20at%20Kholen%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20on%20December%202%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20farmers%20cited%20the%20declining%20productivity%20in%20jhum%20fields%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20income%20generated%20was%20insufficient%20to%20feed%20even%20an%20average%20family%20throughout%20the%20year.%20Coupled%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20alternative%20sources%20of%20livelihood%2C%20these%20farmers%20resorted%20to%20poppy%20cultivation%20to%20meet%20their%20needs%20and%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kipgen%20wrote.%20%26quot%3B...%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20forced%20eradication%20of%20poppy%20cultivation%20instigated%20by%20the%20government%20officials%20is%20a%20more%20problematic%20approach%20as%20it%20can%20escalate%20social%20tensions%2C%20and%20also%20create%20animosity%20between%20the%20local%20government%20and%20farmer%20communities%2C%20which%20would%20hinder%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20despite%20initiating%20such%20programmes%2C%20the%20state%20government%20of%20Manipur%20is%20yet%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20promises%20-%20to%20provide%20assistance%2C%20compensation%2C%20and%20alternative%20livelihoods%20to%20farmers.%20Without%20this%2C%20farmers%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20escape%20from%20the%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20poppy%20cultivation.%20Eradicating%20poppy%20cultivation%20necessitates%20providing%20farmers%20with%20incentives%20such%20as%20subsidies%2C%20technical%20assistance%2C%20and%20agricultural%20inputs%20in%20order%20to%20persuade%20them%20to%20stop%20growing%20opium%20poppy%20and%20instead%20shift%20to%20alternative%20or%20sustainable%20means%20of%20livelihoods%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kipgen%20wrote%2C%20citing%20several%20studies%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20blame%20poor%20farmers%20over%20perceived%20harm%20to%20natural%20systems%20is%20an%20inaccurate%20way%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20problem%2C%20a%20researcher%20of%20land%20conflict%20who%20has%20been%20studying%20issues%20linked%20to%20forests%20in%20Manipur%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20poor%20who%20work%20as%20labourers%20on%20poppy%20fields%20they%20don't%20own%20do%20so%20out%20of%20compulsion.%20They%20need%20help.%20Marginal%20farmers%20who%20moved%20to%20poppy%20after%20many%20years%20of%20normal%20crop%20failure%20require%20help.%20But%20jail%20is%20the%20only%20place%20for%20the%20rich%20who%20encourage%20growing%20poppy%20for%20narcotics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20researcher%2C%20asking%20not%2