%20Israel%20amid%20the%20latter's%20war%20on%20Hamas.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20said%20most%20of%20the%20200-plus%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20cruise%20missiles%20and%20attack%20drones%2C%20were%20intercepted%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Israel's%20allies%20before%20landing.%20Teheran%20said%20it%20was%20an%20act%20of%20%26quot%3Bself-defence%26quot%3B%20after%20Iran's%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20Damascus%20was%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20situation%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%26quot%3B%20tragedy%2C%20New%20Delhi%20said%20it%20is%20seriously%20concerned%20about%20the%20escalation%20of%20hostilities%20which%20threatens%20the%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20call%20for%20immediate%20de-escalation%2C%20exercise%20of%20restraint%2C%20stepping%20back%20from%20violence%20and%20return%20to%20the%20path%20of%20diplomacy.%20We%20are%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20evolving%20situation...%20It%20is%20vital%20that%20security%20and%20stability%20are%20maintained%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20has%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20escalation%C2%A0%20was%20expected%20since%20Israel%20started%20war%20on%20Hamas.%20Last%20week%2C%20India%20issued%20an%20advisory%20urging%20its%20citizens%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20Iran%20or%20Israel%20and%20asked%20Indians%20living%20in%20either%20country%20to%20observe%20%26quot%3Butmost%20precautions%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%20the%20escalation%20has%20happened%2C%20it%20places%20India%20between%20two%20nations%20with%20which%20it%20shares%20strong%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20strategic%20ties%20with%20Israel%20--%20with%20which%20it%20has%20cooperation%20in%20multiple%20fields%20from%20defence%20to%20technology%20for%20decades%20--%20has%20been%20upscaled%20since%20the%20NDA%20government%20came%20to%20power.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20visited%20Israel%20in%202018%20and%20his%20personal%20chemistry%20with%20PM%20Netanyahu%20is%20very%20good.%20Isarel%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20biggest%20defence%20supplies%20aling%20with%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20France%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20positive%20relationship%20with%20Iran%20is%20older%20%E2%80%93%20the%20country%20being%20one%20of%20India's%20prime%20supplier%20of%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20Iran's%20second-largest%20importer%20of%20oil%20before%20the%20sanctions%20were%20imposed%20over%20its%20controversial%20nuclear%20programme.%C2%A0%20For%20four%20years%2C%20India%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20buy%20oil%20from%20Iran%2C%20but%20the%20two%20had%20remained%20close.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndia%20and%20Iran%20concluded%20a%20defence%20pact%20in%202002.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20went%20for%20a%20visit%20to%20Iran%2C%20where%20India%20is%20invested%20in%20building%20the%20Chabahar%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20does%20not%20consider%20Hamas%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel%20which%20triggered%20retaliation%2C%20was%20considered%20a%20terrorist%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20--%20the%20first%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20visit%20Israel%20--%20had%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20act%26quot%3B%20through%20a%20tweet.%20Through%20this%2C%20India%20has%20given%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20it%20is%20with%20Israel%20against%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20has%20been%20raising%20its%20voice%20regarding%20the%20humanitarian%20tragedy%20in%20Gaza.%20New%20Delhi%2C%20which%20has%20been%20advocating%20a%20two-state%20solution%2C%20continues%20to%20help%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713103800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fl2gkkkcg_israeliran_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-indias-stand-amid-threat-of-open-war-between-ir