2%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Residents%20Can%20Do%20a%20Lot%20More%20to%20Save%20The%20City%E2%80%99s%20Water%20%26amp%3B%20It%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20Too%20Late%20to%20Start%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(In%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346640%2Fbengaluru-water-scarcity-crisis-solutions-lake-revival-open-wells-rainwater-harvesting-treated-wastewater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPart%201%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%20series%2C%20we%20discussed%20a%20variety%20of%20problems%20and%20solutions%20on%20a%20policy%20level%20about%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20current%20water%20crisis%2C%20addressing%20issues%20ranging%20from%20state%20failure%20to%20reviving%20lakes%2C%20recharging%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%2C%20building%20open%20recharge%20wells%2C%20and%20using%20treated%20wastewater%20as%20a%20genuine%20resource.%20Here%20we%E2%80%99ll%20discuss%20what%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20help!)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20issues%20of%20state%20capacity%20and%20the%20need%20to%20recalibrate%20water%20policy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20mitigate%20the%20water%20scarcity%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296593%2Fbengaluru-floods-zenrainman-s-vishwanath-expert-shares-water-logging-solutions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%20Vishwanath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20civil%20engineer%20and%20urban%20planner%20with%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20water%20and%20sanitation%20sector%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20consume%20less%20water%2C%20recycle%20greywater%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20to%20minimise%20my%20demand%2C%20then%20there%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20water%20which%20I%20can%20save%20within%20my%20whole%20zone.%20And%20the%20administration%20can%20transfer%20some%20of%20my%20zone%E2%80%99s%20water%20to%20another%20which%20is%20facing%20scarcity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20living%20in%20the%20affected%20area%2C%20especially%20in%20apartment%20complexes%20with%2020%20units%20or%20more%20(that%20are%20mandated%20to%20have%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%2C%20Vishwanath%20believes%20that%20if%20they%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants%20are%20running%20well%2C%20then%20they%20can%20fulfil%20all%20their%20non-potable%20water%20requirements%20from%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20residents%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20well%2C%20their%20borewells%20will%20have%20water.%20If%20the%20community%20works%20around%20the%20lakes%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20comes%20together%2C%20and%20makes%20sure%20that%20the%20lake%20is%20cleaned%20up%20and%20de-silted%20along%20with%20the%20State%2C%20then%20these%20water%20bodies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20their%20STPs%20that%20are%20well%20treated%20can%20be%20led%20into%20these%20lakes%20so%20that%20it%20recharges%20the%20aquifers.%20I%20believe%20these%20are%20all%20the%20steps%20that%20citizens%20have%20to%20take%20to%20protect%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20steps%20has%20he%20taken%20in%20his%20own%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20being%20mindful%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20you%20consume%2C%20you%20can%20deploy%20technologies%20like%20aerators%20on%20your%20taps%20or%20shower%20heads.%20You%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20water%20you%20collect%20after%20cleaning%20your%20dishes%20is%20used%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20or%20the%20garden%20that%20you%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20case%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20all%20the%20greywater%20is%20recycled.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20collect%20the%20wastewater%20from%20my%20washing%20machine%20and%20half-bucket%20bath%20water.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F230971%2Fnagaland-small-biz-entrepreneur-woman-organic-soaps-oils-skincare-personal-care-eco-friendly-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20soaps%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20detergents%20which%20do%20not%20have%20phosphates%20and%20phthalates.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20wastewater%20from%20bathing%20or%20washing%20clothes%20can%20be%20used%20for%20swabbing%20the%20floor%2C%20watering%20the%20terrace%20garden%2C%20and%20cleaning%20the%20car.%20I%20have%20a%20dry%20compost%20toilet%20which%20requires%20no%20water%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20may%20seem%20a%20bit%20extreme%20to%20some%20but%20it%20has%20worked%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F92434%2Fa-r-shivakumar-rainwater-harvesting-bengaluru-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20that%20are%20operating%20optimally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20last%20rains%20in%20the%20city%20were%20in%20November%2C%20our%201%2C000-litre%20rain%20barrel%20still%20has%20enough%20water%20for%20our%20drinking%20and%20cooking%20needs%20till%20June.%20I%20have%20taken%20away%20plants%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20grown%20and%20left%20the%20garden%20to%20be%20dry%20so%20that%20when%20the%20rains%20come%2C%20I%20can%20restart%20my%20garden.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20only%20have%20drought-tolerant%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20use%20less%20energy%20(electricity).%20The%20less%20energy%20I%20use%2C%20the%20more%20water%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20in%20some%20dam%20or%20thermal%20power%20plant.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20energy%20you%20use%20and%20about%20the%20food%20you%20eat%20so%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20waste%20it.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20steps%20I%20have%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FyyRNm-mFn7g%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FyyRNm-mFn7g%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20can%20I%20reduce%20my%20water%20consumption%20by%2050%25%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20points%20mentioned%20by%20Vishwanath%20in%20reducing%20his%20water%20consumption%20was%20the%20use%20of%20aerators.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20simplest%20hacks%20you%20can%20adopt%20in%20your%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20Shashidhara%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20EverythingECO%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20startup%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20water%20and%20waste%20management.%20Among%20the%20products%20EverythingECO%20manufactures%20are%20aerators%20that%20you%20can%20attach%20to%20washroom%20or%20kitchen%20taps%20and%20restrictors%20for%20shower%20heads%20and%20health%20faucets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKarunaprasada%20Kanavi%20and%20I%20started%20EverythingECO%20with%20a%20vision%20in%202016%20to%20bring%20sustainability%20to%20businesses%20and%20homes%2C%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20water%20and%20waste%20management.%20Before%20getting%20into%20business%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20how%20people%20and%20different%20businesses%20were%20using%20water%2C%20what%20their%20daily%20consumption%20levels%20were%2C%20and%20started%20thinking%20of%20customised%20solutions%20required%20for%20each%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Save%20water%20in%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FEverythingEco-Co-Founders-1712574865-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346781%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashidhara%20Kumaraswamy%20%26amp%3B%20Karunaprasada%20Kanavi%2C%20co-founders%20of%20EverythingEco.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shashidhara%20and%20his%20co-founder%20did%20a%20detailed%20audit%20on%20water%20consumption%20levels%20across%20multiple%20locations%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20they%20found%20that%20each%20business%20or%20residential%20unit%20has%20specific%20requirements%20based%20on%20its%20usage%20pattern.%20In%20certain%20locations%2C%20they%20found%20the%20flow%20rate%20measured%20in%20hand%20washing%20taps%20to%20be%20around%2015%20to%2016%20litres%20per%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%2C%20we%20have%20observed%20that%20when%20you%20buy%20taps%20of%20standard%20fittings%2C%20their%20flow%20rate%20is%20between%2014%20to%2018%20litres%20per%20minute%20based%20on%20water%20pressure.%20Most%20fixtures%20sold%20commercially%20do%20not%20have%20any%20aerators.%20They%20come%20with%20filters%20to%20filter%20out%20the%20dust.%20These%20filters%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20the%20job%20of%20water%20conservation%2C%20but%20only%20ensure%20the%20laminar%20flow%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuring%20this%20audit%2C%20they%20concluded%20that%20taps%20for%20hand%20washing%20should%20never%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%203%20litres%20per%20minute.%20Similarly%2C%20for%20kitchens%2C%20they%20understood%20that%20people%20required%20a%20higher%20flow%20rate%20but%20not%20more%20than%206%20to%208%20litres%20per%20minute.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20ideal%20scenario%2C%20no%20tap%20should%20have%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%20more%20than%206%20litres%20a%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20look%20at%20multiple%20use%20cases%20in%20terms%20of%20hospitals%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20bulk%20washing%20areas%2C%20their%20requirements%20are%20very%20different%20and%20not%20everyone%20can%20live%20with%20spray%20taps%20releasing%203%20litres%20a%20minute.%20We%20started%20looking%20at%20custom%20designs%20and%20solutions.%20Our%20company%20does%20comprehensive%20water%20audits%20for%20businesses%20and%20provides%20solutions%20for%20varied%20sizes%20of%20taps%2C%20addressing%20diverse%20types%20of%20flow%20rates%20that%20are%20required%2C%20and%20implementing%20them%20end-to-end%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAerators%20manufactured%20by%20EverythingECO%20start%20with%20flow%20rates%20(per%20minute)%20of%201%20litre%2C%203%20litres%2C%204%20litres%2C%20and%206%20litres.%20%E2%80%9CAerators%20with%20a%20flow%20rate%20of%200.5%20and%201%20litre%20per%20minute%20usually%20offer%20a%20mist-type%20flow.%20But%20for%20commercial%20and%20residential%20apartments%2C%20this%20flow%20rate%20is%20too%20low%20to%20wash%20hands.%20For%20hand%20wash%20taps%2C%20our%20aerator%20which%20restricts%20flow%20rates%20to%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20is%20popular%20across%20all%20sectors.%20Many%20people%20opt%20for%203%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerator%20for%20their%20kitchen%20taps%20as%20well%2C%20because%20it%20effectively%20covers%20a%20larger%20area%20for%20washing%20utensils.%20If%20customers%20want%20laminar%20flow%20in%20their%20kitchen%20taps%2C%20then%20they%20go%20for%204%20or%206%20litres%20a%20minute%20aerators%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shashidhara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRestrictors%20reduce%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20from%20the%20pipes%20or%20the%20entry%20points.%20You%20can%20attach%20these%20restrictors%20to%20older%20type%20taps%2C%20health%20faucets%20and%20shower%20heads%20and%20reduce%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%20anywhere%20between%206%20to%209%20litres%20a%20minute.%20Depending%20on%20the%20water%20pressure%20of%20their%20shower%20heads%2C%20people%20can%20use%20restrictors%20to%20limit%20the%20flow%20rate%20to%206%20to%209%20litres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%2