nd%20the%20date%20bunches%20to%20protect%20from%20birds%2C%20which%20can%20eat%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20sturdy%2C%20the%20date%20palms%20do%20not%20attract%20any%20pests%20and%20diseases%2C%20so%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20input%20costs.%20All%20they%20require%20is%20water%20for%20irrigation%2C%20manure%2C%20and%20protection%20from%20birds%2C%20which%20can%20eat%20the%20fruit.%20So%2C%20I%20wrap%20a%20net%20around%20the%20date%20bunches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20Mukesh%20mentions%20that%20dates%20require%20manual%20pollination.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20male%20and%20female%20species%20in%20date%20palms%20grow%20as%20separate%20trees.%20The%20males%20produce%20pollen%20from%20flowers%20and%20require%20manual%20pollination%20with%20females%20which%20bear%20fruits.%20For%20every%20100%20female%20plants%2C%20you%20need%204-6%20male%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20flowering%20season%20in%20February%2C%20these%20fruit%20varieties%20ripen%20before%20monsoon%20and%20the%20produce%20is%20harvested%20by%20June-July%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Mukesh%20has%20also%20created%20a%20pond%20where%20he%20harvests%20up%20to%203%20lakh%20litres%20of%20rainwater.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20rainwater%20is%20an%20elixir%20for%20our%20dates%20as%20it%20contains%20nutrients%20like%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20potassium%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20This%20also%20helps%20me%20save%2020-25%20percent%20on%20irrigation%20in%20the%20dry%20region.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20use%20drip%20irrigation%20that%20takes%20water%20directly%20to%20the%20roots%20through%20pipes%20and%20minimises%20water%20wastage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20date%20cultivation%2C%20he%20says%20any%20farmer%20can%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20least%2060%20date%20palms%20can%20be%20planted%20in%20an%20acre%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20can%20be%20earned%20from%20each%20tree.%20About%20250%20kg%20of%20fruits%20can%20be%20harvested%20from%20one%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20has%20250%20date%20palms%20and%20earned%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20in%20the%20last%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mukesh%20has%20received%20immense%20recognition%20at%20the%20state%20and%20district%20levels%20for%20growing%20dates%20organically.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-2-1712555378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMukesh%20has%20received%20immense%20recognition%20at%20the%20state%20and%20district%20levels%20for%20growing%20dates%20organically.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sells%20all%20his%20produce%20to%20about%20120%20consumers%20based%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Noida%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20he%20has%20received%20immense%20recognition%20at%20the%20state%20and%20district%20levels%20for%20growing%20dates%20organically.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20was%20felicitated%20for%20the%20promotion%20of%20indigenous%20breeds%20of%20cows%20for%20