%20named%20after%20Lady%20Canning%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Twitter%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvernaculartube%2Fstatus%2F1515703329284042754%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAjatshatru%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredited%20with%20creating%20the%20%3Cem%3Eledikeni%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20Bengali%20sweet%2C%20this%20sweet%20shop%2C%20over%20two%20centuries%20old%2C%20has%20watched%20the%20city%20evolve%20into%20its%20present%20form.%20At%20the%20turn%20of%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20as%20reform%20and%20renaissance%20were%20rife%20in%20Bengal%2C%20sweet%20shops%20began%20mushrooming%20across%20the%20city.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20Paran%20Chandra%20Nag%2C%20too%2C%20decided%20to%20channel%20his%20skills%20into%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20making%20at%20his%20shop%20in%20Bowbazar%2C%20Kolkata.%20Starting%20in%201826%2C%20this%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333208%2Fwhere-to-eat-in-kolkata-classics-best-heritage-eateries-map-anindya-basu-dolon-dutta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20seasoned%20sweet%20shop%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20to%20amass%20a%20great%20crowd%2C%20and%20among%20them%20was%20Sir%20Ashutosh%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3ELifestyle%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%20tells%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20Lady%20Canning%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20then%20viceroy%20of%20India%2C%20Charles%20John%20Canning%2C%20was%20once%20visiting%20erstwhile%20Calcutta%20in%201858%20and%20wanted%20a%20special%20sweet%20made%20for%20her%20birthday.%20Nag%20took%20up%20the%20challenge!%20And%20it%20is%20this%20creation%20that%20was%20named%20after%20Lady%20Canning%2C%20which%20over%20the%20years%20became%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eledikeni%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Flury%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hub%20that